this was shot by @itrevormoore back in 2021 as proof of concept for a show we were going to pitch. we were almost finished editing it (by “we” i mean me watching trevor edit after lunch from poquito mas) when we lost trevor. it took me a long time before i felt like even thinking about working on this again, but knew it had to be done, if only to share one of the last things trevor helped to create. in an act of exceptional generosity trevor’s wife aimee was able to recover the footage from his laptop. with the help from my incredibly talented friend @claytatum we finished the edit in a way i think trevor would truly enjoy. hope you like it and thanks again for all your support. 

and yes, wayne will have his own show eventually, i promise to make it happen!
